assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Guangdong Dtech Technology Co., Ltd. engages in the research and development, production, and sells of tools, materials, and equipment in China. It offers PCB micro-drilling bits; routers, such as hypotenust, chamfering, and engraving tools, as well as spiral endmill, CBF, RHF, RCF, and ET series products; CNC cutting tools; automatic grinding machines; picosecond laser cutting machines; automatic UV laser making machines; double platform automatic pasting and reinforcing machines; single platform automatic patching and reinforcing machines; abrasive ring belts; ceramic, titanium drum abrasive, nylon, stainless steel platen cleaning, leveling wheel, high-density, high-cut, FH, and FD foaming brushes; various film products; and PCB consumables. The company's products have applications in PCB, 3C, auto parts, molds, and other industries. It exports its products to Europe, the United States, South Korea, Southeast Asia, and internationally. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Dongguan, China.
